Package edu.kit.ipd.are.archdoclink.nlp

Interface NaturalLanguageProcessing

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ParseProcessing
    public interface NaturalLanguageProcessing
    Interface for NaturalLanguageProcessing. Classes implementing this interface can be used to process texts or Documents.

    Jan Keim

        Optional<? extends Phrase> getPhraseOfWord​(Word word)
        Returns the Phrase the given word is contained in. If the word is not contained in any phrase, an empty Optional is returned.
        Parameters:
        word - Word that should be looked for in Phrases
        Returns:
        Optional containing the Phrase the given word is contained in. Empty Optional if word is not contained in any phrase.
